regionGB_up.title: Aero Sudah Terbaru
regionGB_up.description:
WhatsApp Base:  2.25.11.79

📜[New] Enable the ability to send direct messages to people who viewed your status.
📜[New] Enable the ability to turn off video before accepting incoming video calls.
📜[New] Enable the ability to add social media links to your profile.
📜[New] Enable the ability to automatically post statuses to other Meta platforms, such as Instagram and Facebook.
📜[New] Enable many other features.
📜[Improved] Anti-ban protection.
 Stability and performance improvements.
 [More] other new features. Enjoy and discover what's new for yourself!

🔗 More fixes and other improvements.
